title: Looking for these T206s in P/F/G
author: Cozumeleno

posts.post_title: Looking for these T206s in P/F/G
posts.post_content:
Need low-quality T206s of these cards and looking to pay $8.00 - $12.00 each. Not looking for absolute beaters missing huge chunks of the card, but common backs and cards with numerous creases and some writing/paper loss is okay.

Someone messaged me about a Bridwell beater, but I got the message on my phone and accidentally deleted it. Please message again, if you would - I am interested.

Thanks
